VARIABLES.NAME: id
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The Generalization ID, this is used to update this table with new predictions

VARIABLES.NAME: size
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The maximum size of the generalization table

VARIABLES.NAME: top_label
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The top label from the generalization table

VARIABLES.NAME: top_probability
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The top probability that is related to the top label from the generalization table

VARIABLES.NAME: probabilities
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: Array of probabilities, each dedicated for each label.
